<html><body><p>Please note if you're using Emacs 24 on OS X 10.7.3, you need `M-x gud-gdb` instead `M-x gdb` to start debug session. </p> <p> It's because `M-x gdb` assume gdb 7.x installed while there is actually only gdb 6.3 installed. </p><ul> <li>C-x C-a C-d gud-remove </li> <li>C-x C-a C-b gud-break </li> <li>C-x C-a C-g gud-run (customized by me) </li> <li>C-x C-a C-p gud-print </li> <li>C-x C-a C-r gud-continue </li> </ul>  </body></html>